snippet.title: City Limits - City Builder Gameplay
snippet.description:
City Limits is a relaxing tile-based puzzle game where you build cities on a desolate island. Place tiles strategically to create a cascading spread of new structures. Cover the island as efficiently as you can before the land becomes unusable. There are no "game overs". Just chill and build.

Wishlist now!

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2056550/City_Limits/
Twitter Page: https://twitter.com/SpaceMyFriend
